    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Does the Prime Minister expect to be in a position to make a statement before the House rises for the summer vacation?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-dc9fcf15-d143-4420-9c0b-f1749298ad2a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
